WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Galu Gary.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
A galu Gary oedd hi.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
A dyna oedd o'r eglan.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.000
A dyna gobeithio, fi'n gwerthu'i carpa grisiaid o.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:13.000
A dyna ni'n boi i weithio so gynnarbon fel fynd yn ddyl.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.000
A sut wnaethwch ddewis yw bach?

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.000
I ddynag, beth gyn ti ar fers yna?

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Fel mae gennych chi carpa grisiaid, cofio dytho.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:26.000
A cofio chyna'r rady o dda ni de.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Reit, be di hidd o?

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
Dyna Gary.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Fel ond ni'n ddweud rhywbeth.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:36.000
Rhyw ddeud a gris.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.000
A bydi a led o? Fela.

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:43.000
A fe'n di fela nhw.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:45.000
O, diwis ganddi'n tapio sfermio fi.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.000
Felly, ller grisiaid o Gary.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.000
